WEBVTT


00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:02.000
I'm asking, do you have any empathy

00:00:02.000 --> 00:00:03.360
with the Palestinian position?

00:00:03.360 --> 00:00:05.440
I have zero empathy

00:00:05.440 --> 00:00:09.120
to people the time after time refuse to.

00:00:09.120 --> 00:00:10.000
To recognize

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:11.920
the right of the Jewish state to their homeland.

00:00:11.920 --> 00:00:13.120
Jewish people in their homeland.

00:00:13.120 --> 00:00:14.120
I have zero sympathy

00:00:14.120 --> 00:00:15.520
because I want to.

00:00:15.520 --> 00:00:17.880
To live in a world where we can live together.

00:00:17.880 --> 00:00:19.020
How can they deny?

00:00:19.080 --> 00:00:19.760
But they deny.

