You have no

00:00:21.040 --> 00:00:23.180
zero empathy in your own words

00:00:23.280 --> 00:00:24.320
with those people?

00:00:24.320 --> 00:00:25.280
No, it's not what I said.

00:00:25.280 --> 00:00:27.480
I said I have zero sympathy to the fact

00:00:27.480 --> 00:00:28.360
that they lost their land.

00:00:28.360 --> 00:00:29.520
They didn't lost their land.

00:00:29.520 --> 00:00:32.780
They committed the crime of attacking the small.

00:00:33.200 --> 00:00:34.840
The small state of Israel were

00:00:34.840 --> 00:00:35.920
after the UN decision.

00:00:35.920 --> 00:00:37.040
So there is no. That.

00:00:37.040 --> 00:00:37.480
The truth is

00:00:37.480 --> 00:00:38.440
there is no empathy.

00:00:38.440 --> 00:00:41.120
I have empathy for the tragedy of the leadership.

00:00:41.120 --> 00:00:42.840
Yes, I have empathy that they are under

00:00:42.840 --> 00:00:44.160
the tragedy of their leadership.

00:00:44.160 --> 00:00:45.960
This is a very hopeless conversation

00:00:45.960 --> 00:00:46.680
